    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented here is a rare opportunity to own a museum-grade vehicle in truly pristine condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still retains its original showroom aroma. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule and a fully documented service history. It has been exclusively garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather, resulting in a spotless undercarriage. This is a turn-key example for the collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
